Summary: UFO near the Grand Teton Mountains.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on a sight-seeing trip when I stopped at a rest area to take the attached photo of the Teton Mountains. At the time I took the photo, neither I nor my traveling partner noticed the UFO object. I do not believe it was visible to the naked eye. If it had been, we would have surely noticed it. We were both facing the mountain range. We did not hear any sounds either. The photo was taken with a digital camera in mid-afternoon. The sky was a little hazy and nearly cloudless. I noticed the object in the photo after I returned home and was viewing the photos on my computer.
